						<a class="title" href="javascript:;" onclick="togglePostFold(event,732289)"></a> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bleggs" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(414493); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=414493&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610227335" alt="bleggs" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=414493)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bleggs" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(414493); return false;" >bleggs</a></span>, <span class="odate time_1269362351 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">23 Mar 2010 16:39</span>
		</div>
