					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/adminbright" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(224440); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=224440&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610227335" alt="AdminBright" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=224440)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/adminbright" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(224440); return false;" >AdminBright</a></span> <span class="odate time_1269366829 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">23 Mar 2010 17:53</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-732350">
									

<p>ARCs are not made specificlally for stories, they are old SCPs that were generally once popular, but have faded in popularity due to the different direction our site has taken. They have been used in stories that didn't feel the need to explain them, since we had the SCPs on site. Nowadays, anyone atemtpting to write and SCP, then write a story about it to keep it, would be laughed off the site.</p>

							</div>

